start.say: Hi, this is Alex with Health America. How are you today?

reason_for_call.say: The reason I’m calling is to follow up on the health information we sent you. Did you get that okay?

qualify_intro.say: Let’s go through your health concerns so I can match the right formulas.

q1_joint.say: Do you have arthritis or joint stiffness?

value_story_pitch.say: Based on your answers, I’ll recommend support for each issue: joints, heart health, and sleep. We always start with multi-issue care to maximize results.

package_offer.say: Best value is our 12-month plan—maximum savings, maximum results. Does that work for you?

offer_6mo.say: Second option is the 6-month supply—great savings. Would you like that?

offer_3mo.say: We can also do a 3-month bundle—solid results and easier on budget. Sound good?

offer_single.say: Finally, we can begin with a single bottle at $49. Does that work?

identity_intro.say: Great, I’ll confirm your details as we go.

name_on_card.say: Full name as on the card?

shipping_same.say: Is the shipping address same as billing?

payment_method.say: Which payment method works best, card or bank?

price_total.say: Your total is {{human_price}}, with no shipping fees or taxes. You’re fully covered by our satisfaction guarantee: if you’re not happy, you call me and I’ll make you whole.

capture_sale.say: Great—let me get that processed for you.

closing_sale.say: Your order is confirmed. Shipping in 5–7 days, thank you for choosing Health America. If you need anything, call us at 1-866-379-5131.

catch_all.say: Could you repeat that another way so I can help?
